    "UIName": "Manticore Heavy Tank (3055 Upgrade)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Manticore Heavy Tank (3055 Upgrade)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>240 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Manticore is one of the most powerful and well-designed tanks ever created. While not matching the raw firepower of super-heavy vehicles like the Demolisher or Behemoth, its combination of heavy armor and diverse weaponry makes it a highly effective platform against most threats.\n\nManufactured by NETC in 3060, this variant replaces the Streak SRM-2 from Defiance's upgrade with a Medium Pulse Laser. It mounts an LB 10-X AC and a Streak SRM-6 in the turret, providing a powerful combination of firepower.",
